    "what_it_measures": "Diffusion index of new orders, production, employment, inventories, prices. ISM. Monthly, 1st business day 10:00 ET. >50 = expansion.\n",
    "why_it_matters": "Baumohl's #2 most stock-sensitive indicator. New Orders subindex is the most forward-looking component; leads headline by ~3 months. ISM Mfg <48 for 3+ months historically signals earnings contraction.\n",
